The paper describes an algorithm for capturing frequency information for streams of arbitrary sequences of symbols in real time. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of the CountMin sketch as the basis for the algorithm suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category of sketching algorithms (cs.SI).
